{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d1efefff-fafa-4139-b266-821f764778fd", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d1efefff-fafa-4139-b266-821f764778fd@1.pkg/1772597623023/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597623710", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d1efefff-fafa-4139-b266-821f764778fd@1.pkg/1772597623023/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597623710"}, "identifier": "d1efefff-fafa-4139-b266-821f764778fd", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>本题考查国家利益至上。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>C：放弃个人利益过于绝对，说法不正确。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>D：人身价值的实现有多种途径，&ldquo;只有&hellip;&hellip;才&rdquo;的说法过于绝对，说法不正确。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A：&ldquo;同损害国家利益的行为作斗争&rdquo;说法与题干无关。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）黄旭华的一生是一场&ldquo;舍得&rdquo;的哲学。他舍了天伦之乐，却以忠尽孝；舍了世俗名利，却以功报国。他隐姓埋名30年，为国防事业立下不朽功勋。他的事迹告诉我们（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）黄旭华的一生是一场“舍得”的哲学。他舍了天伦之乐，却以忠尽孝；舍了世俗名利，却以功报国。他隐姓埋名30年，为国防事业立下不朽功勋。他的事迹告诉我们（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d1efefff-fafa-4139-b266